snippet.textDisplay: Girl, your labor and delivery reminded me of mine! I also got induced cause I had gallstones. And was in labor for 2 days. My team kept telling me if your body doesn't hit 10cm by 10pm I had to have an emergency c-section cause I stayed at 9cm for 3hrs. but with the grace of god I made it to 10cm and pushed for 3 1/2 hrs and gave birth at 12:25am. I had pre-eclampsia and hemorrhaged right after so I didn't get to hold my baby until they got the bleeding in control and got a blood transfusion right away. I'm so happy for your little family and your precious blessing. Your story literally gave me major flash backs.
